      "acceptanceCriteria": "Constitutive model selection justified with literature support; titanium alloy Ti-6Al-4V elastic-plastic representation validated against coupon data.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening model for Ti-6Al-4V screw and rod selected based on published coupon test data (Froes 2015). UHMWPE block modeled as linear elastic within working load range per ASTM F1717 guidance. Model form appropriate for static compression-bending regime."
