      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from traceable coupon tests or peer-reviewed literature; geometric inputs derived from CMM measurements of physical specimens.",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and tangent modulus (2.1 GPa) from manufacturer-supplied coupon data corroborated by ASM Handbook values. Screw geometry from CMM measurements of three production screws; mean dimensions used. Input uncertainty propagated via ±10% material property perturbation study."
