      "rationale": "E/uval computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 9 for stiffness (0.87), yield force (1.12), and force at 40 mm (1.61). All values below 1.96 threshold. Percent differences also below 10% pre-specified bound. Output comparison level 3 achieved."
