      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in ASTM F1717 and directly referenced in FDA guidance for spinal implant 510(k) submissions. QoI relevance to clinical failure modes (fatigue initiation at yield, construct loosening) established in published literature. Relevance level 3 achieved."
